OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FSeveral new charges have been made
OL,8,Famid an investigation into reports of
OL,9,Fchild abuse at a former children's
OL,10,Fcentre in Monmouthshire, police say.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,13,Fhas authorised 26 further charges
OL,14,Fagainst Angus Riddell and Robin
OL,15,FGriffiths who were previously charged
OL,16,Fwith 45 counts between them.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
