OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294630
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FRiddell, 69, of Cwmbach, Rhondda Cynon
OL,8,FTaf, was arrested on 24 February and
OL,9,Fhas been charged with a further 21
OL,10,Foffences. They are two counts of rape
OL,11,Fof a female under 16, one count of
OL,12,Fgross indecency with a girl under 14
OL,13,Fyears of age, three counts of indecent
OL,14,Fassault on a girl under the age of 16
OL,15,Fyears, one count of indecent assault
OL,16,Fon boy under the age of 14 years and
OL,17,F14 counts of assault/ill-treatment/
OL,18,Fneglect/abandon a child/young person
OL,19,Fto cause unnecessary suffering/injury.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
