PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294631
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FRiddell was previously charged with 38
OL,8,Foffences in June 2025.
OL,10,FRobin Griffiths, 66, from Blaenau
OL,11,FGwent originally but now lives in
OL,12,FBideford, Devon, was arrested on 23
OL,13,FFebruary and has been charged with a
OL,14,Ffurther five offences. They are three
OL,15,Fcounts of indecent assault on a boy
OL,16,Funder the age of 14 years and two
OL,17,Fcounts of gross indecency with a boy
OL,18,Funder the age of 14 years of age.
OL,20,FGriffiths was previously charged with
OL,21,Fseven offences in June 2025.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
