CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294631
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FBoth are on bail and are due to appear
OL,8,Fbefore magistrates in March in
OL,9,Frelation to the new charges.
OL,11,FThe two defendants have previously
OL,12,Fplead not guilty to the initial
OL,13,Fcharges at previous court hearings,
OL,14,Fand a trial date of January 2027 has
OL,15,Fbeen set.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
