CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294631
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FOperation Spinney has been
OL,8,Finvestigating reports made by a number
OL,9,Fof men and women of sexual and
OL,10,Fphysical abuse committed against them
OL,11,Fas children predominantly at the
OL,12,Fformer Coed Glas Assessment Centre,
OL,13,FAbergavenny, between the 1970s and
OL,14,F1990s.
OL,16,FThe centre at the time was the
OL,17,Fresponsibility of the former Gwent
OL,18,FLocal Authority and has been closed
OL,19,Fsince 1995.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
