PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294631
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FDetective Chief Superintendent Andrew
OL,8,FTuck of Gwent Police said: "Our focus
OL,9,Fremains on supporting victims in this
OL,10,Finvestigation and supporting them
OL,11,Falongside specialist agencies.
OL,13,F"We continue to work closely with the
OL,14,FCrown Prosecution Service and local
OL,15,Fauthorities as part of this long-
OL,16,Frunning investigation.
OL,26,@pD@\OUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
