PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294631
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"We take all reports of child abuse
OL,8,Fseriously and would urge anyone who
OL,9,Fhas suffered abuse or has concerns
OL,10,Fabout someone who may be suffering to
OL,11,Fcome forward and speak to the police.
OL,12,FWe will listen to you and investigate
OL,13,Fall offences and also ensure you have
OL,14,Faccess to any help or support you
OL,15,Fneed."
OL,17,FEarlier this month, CPS authorised
OL,18,Fcharges against two other people in
OL,19,Fconnection with the investigation with
OL,20,Fsix offences between them.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@FO]
