CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772294631
OL,3,C26 new charges amid investigation into
OL,4,Cchild abuse at a former children's
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FLisa Gething, a 59-year-old woman from
OL,8,FAbergavenny, a social worker employed
OL,9,Fby Caerphilly County Borough Council,
OL,10,Fwas charged with four counts of
OL,11,Fassault/ill-treat/neglect/abandon a
OL,12,Fchild/young person to cause
OL,13,Funnecessary suffering/injury.
OL,15,FAnd Simon Bevan, a 55-year-old
OL,16,FCaerphilly man was charged with two
OL,17,Fcounts of the same offence. They are
OL,18,Falso on bail and set to appear at
OL,19,FNewport Crown Court on Friday 27
OL,20,FFebruary.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
